      "role": "user",
      "content": "Okay, that makes sense. So if the pH drops too low, it basically stunts the process. What happens if I increase the hydration levels? Does a wetter starter change the rate at which these microorganisms move through the substrate or affect how the enzymes interact with the starch?",
